node.contents: So here's what to do to get this file run. In the Package explorer, create a new project, call it whatever you want. Tell it to add a source directory. After is added, right click on the source directory and add a package called 'example', then right click on 'example' and tell it to create a class called MainDemo with public static void main stubbed out. If that runs, you're in good shape, just clear that file's contents with your program.
